// Array operators -

/**
 * $push - inserts an element at the end of array
 * $addToSet - add an element if it doesn't exist in array, won't push element if it already exists
 * $pull - removes a matching element from array
 * $pullAll - remove multiple matching elements from array
 * $pop (1/-1) - removes the last or first element from array
 */

